      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>210 - Abbreviated Title (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2003</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td width="45%"><strong>First Indicator</strong><br><em>Title added entry</em><br>0 - No added entry <br>1 - Added entry <br><br></td>
            <td width="45%"><strong>Second Indicator</strong><br><em>Type</em><br># - Abbreviated key title <br>0 - Other abbreviated title <br><br></td>
