      <hr>
      <h3>FIELD DEFINITION AND SCOPE</h3>
      <p>Title as abbreviated for indexing or identification. An abbreviated <em>key</em> title
         is supplied by ISSN centers, based on the Key Title (Field 222). Other abbreviated
                  titles are supplied by cataloging agencies, including abstracting and indexing
                  services.
      </p>
      <p>Abbreviated title may be created by the agency supplying the field or it may be taken
                     from the piece.      </p>
      <hr>
      <h3>GUIDELINES FOR APPLYING CONTENT DESIGNATORS</h3>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> INDICATORS
      </h4>
      <div class="indicator"><strong>First Indicator - Title added entry</strong> <div class="description">Whether an added entry is to be generated for the title.
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong>0 - No added entry</strong> <div class="description">No title added entry is to be generated.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong>1 - Added entry</strong> <div class="description">Title added entry is to be generated.</div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="indicator"><strong>Second Indicator - Type</strong> <div class="description">Type of abbreviated title.
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong># - Abbreviated key title</strong> <div class="description">Abbreviated title is based on the title contained in field 222 (Key Title). It
                                       is assigned by national centers under the auspices of the ISSN Network in
                                       accordance with ISO 4, <em>Documentation - Rules for the Abbreviation of Title
                                             Words and Titles of Publications</em> and <em>List of Serial Title Word
                                             Abbreviations</em>. The abbreviated key title is an agency-assigned data
                                       element.
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="indicatorvalue"><strong>0 - Other abbreviated title</strong> <div class="description">Abbreviated title is other than an abbreviated key title.</div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> SUBFIELD CODES
      </h4>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$a - Abbreviated title</strong> <div class="description">Complete abbreviated title.</div>
         <div class="example">
