      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Qualifying information</strong> <div class="description">Abbreviated form of the parenthetical qualifying information contained in the key
                              title (field 222).
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">When qualifying information is present in the key title, the same information is
                                 added to field 210 in the appropriate abbreviated form. The qualifier is always
                                 enclosed in parentheses.
            </div>
         </div>
